      "comment": "CAMBLA DIVA (1) box seated early before forging to the lead turning and lifting to score (23.50) at this track in a Free For All over 407m. Got the money at her only try from this box. Form reads well for this. JALAPENO POPPER (2) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into third last time out (24.23) over 407m at this track. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. DISH LIQUOR (6) boasts a strong record this journey with seven wins and two minors from 13 tries. Was out of placings last time (30.09) at this track in a OPEN, finishing seventh and beaten 7 lengths. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. FEDERAL BLUE BOY (4) was in the money last time at Townsville (29.14) in a OPEN, finishing a 10 length third. Has two wins already from this draw.",
